WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:02.534
.

00:02.536 --> 00:06.205
[background chatter]

00:09.109 --> 00:11.276
- Seven years ago today,
lonnie.

00:11.278 --> 00:12.578
Today.

00:12.580 --> 00:14.279
Seven years!

00:14.281 --> 00:16.280
He would have been 15!

00:16.283 --> 00:18.083
But you murdered that boy.

00:18.085 --> 00:19.218
- I'm getting
a restraining order!

00:19.220 --> 00:20.719
- I'm gonna give you
a reason

00:20.721 --> 00:23.355
To need one one day--
you and your sick-ass son!

00:28.194 --> 00:30.562
- Oh, for god's sake.
You're following us now?

00:30.564 --> 00:33.599
- You having fun, lonnie?
Huh?

00:33.601 --> 00:35.401
Life's good, isn't it?

00:35.403 --> 00:37.169
- You're not supposed to be

00:37.171 --> 00:39.071
Within 100 feet of my family.
- Don't touch me.

00:39.073 --> 00:40.439
- No, no, no.
You need to get--

00:40.441 --> 00:42.141
Ugh!
Ohh...

00:45.478 --> 00:47.780
- You all know what he did.

00:47.782 --> 00:50.349
You make me sick.

00:54.621 --> 00:57.322
- And so this brother
comes across the yard.

00:57.324 --> 00:59.425
He's all skeezed out
on crystal or something.

00:59.427 --> 01:02.127
And he says, he says,
"chicken pot pie."

01:02.129 --> 01:04.229
Like I'm supposed to know
what that is, right?

01:04.230 --> 01:06.165
So my boy looks at him,

01:06.167 --> 01:08.333
Points back at the block
and he says,

01:08.335 --> 01:10.202
"that way."

01:10.204 --> 01:12.104
Did not matter
what this cat was on.

01:12.106 --> 01:14.540
He just doubles back to where
he came from lickety-split,

01:14.542 --> 01:16.275
You know what I'm saying?

01:16.277 --> 01:18.277
- Hey, j, listen,
I got some news.

01:18.279 --> 01:20.212
Um...

01:20.214 --> 01:24.149
I had to pull some strings,
but I got you in at the cta.

01:24.151 --> 01:27.786
That's where city workers
send their loser relatives.

01:27.788 --> 01:29.221
- It's a job.

01:29.223 --> 01:34.460
- You know you sound more and
more like him every day, right?

01:34.462 --> 01:36.295
- You start Monday.

01:36.297 --> 01:38.430
- [scoffs]

01:40.800 --> 01:43.135
Okay, pop, sure.

01:43.137 --> 01:46.271
[phone buzzes]

01:46.273 --> 01:48.540
- Excuse me,
I gotta take this.

01:48.542 --> 01:51.510
Hello?

01:51.512 --> 01:54.113
- Strange how
things worked out, huh?

01:54.115 --> 01:55.414
- How's that?

01:55.416 --> 01:58.617
- When we took you in,
you were the problem.

01:58.619 --> 02:00.219
And now you're
the golden girl,

02:00.221 --> 02:01.587
And I'm the prodigal son.

02:01.589 --> 02:04.456
- Well, here we are, justin.

02:04.458 --> 02:06.492
And now you have
a second chance,

02:06.494 --> 02:08.327
So don't piss on it.

02:10.330 --> 02:13.365
- We gotta roll.

02:13.367 --> 02:14.666
I'm sorry, kid.

